.TH "snd_hdac_stream_init" 9 "snd_hdac_stream_init" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
snd_hdac_stream_init \- initialize each stream (aka device)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" snd_hdac_stream_init
.BI "(struct hdac_bus *bus "  ","
.BI "struct hdac_stream *azx_dev "  ","
.BI "int idx "  ","
.BI "int direction "  ","
.BI "int tag "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "bus" 12
HD-audio core bus
.IP "azx_dev" 12
HD-audio core stream object to initialize
.IP "idx" 12
stream index number
.IP "direction" 12
stream direction (SNDRV_PCM_STREAM_PLAYBACK or SNDRV_PCM_STREAM_CAPTURE)
.IP "tag" 12
the tag id to assign
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Assign the starting bdl address to each stream (device) and initialize.
